    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』。アイドルがやっ\nてみたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌のお誕生日企画かぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!” It’s that birthday project\nin the magazine where they grant wishes for idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0024968646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1666659037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私や沙季ちゃんに続いて\n千紗ちゃんにもお話が来たんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Following me and Saki-chan‚\nyou got an offer too‚ Chisa-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2448314037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.7999998092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。でも、いざやることになったら\n何をお願いしようか悩んじゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But now that I’m actually going to do it‚\nI’m having trouble deciding what to wish for…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9923586118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5999991734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "良ければ、渚ちゃんとお姉ちゃんに\n相談したいなって思ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was hoping I could talk to\nNagisa-chan and you about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2333325068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.0666668574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだったのね\n急に話があるって言うから、何かと思っちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s what it was.\nI was wondering what you want to talk about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3666676204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0179594994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、実際悩んじゃうよね\n私も、すぐには思いつかなかったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s understandable that you’d be worried.\nI couldn’t think of anything right away either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2846261661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私の時は、千紗がかわりに考えてくれたわよね\n好きなことを沢山させてもらえて、嬉しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it was my turn‚ Chisa thought of something for me.\nI was happy because I got to do a lot of things I liked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1088694111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.7805219651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗も難しく考えないで、お裁縫とか、ホラー映画とか\n好きなことに関係するお願いをするのはどうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ don’t overthink it. How about making a wish related to\nsomething you like‚ like sewing or horror movies?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3666676204,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}